    <item>
      <title>特朗普检察官法尼·威利斯可以继续审理佐治亚州案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大法官裁定，富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯可以继续监督佐治亚州唐纳德·特朗普的选举干预案，称她与首席检察官的恋爱关系不正当，但并未造成需要撤职的利益冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州法官裁定，如果特别检察官被免职，法尼·威利斯可以继续审理特朗普选举干扰案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-15/urgent-fulton-county-da-fani-willis-must-step-aside-or-remove-special-prosecutor-in-trump-case-judge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大（美联社）——负责监督该案的法官周五裁定，富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯必须退出针对唐纳德·特朗普的佐治亚州选举干预案，或罢免与她有恋爱关系的特别检察官，然后案件才能继续进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-15/urgent-fulton-county-da-fani-willis-must-step-aside-or-remove-special-prosecutor-in-trump-case-judge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:08:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
